&lt;li>这个git &lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack/tree/master/exampleSite/content/post" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>repo&lt;/a>可以看到一些sample post&lt;/li>
&lt;li>这个&lt;a class="link" href="https://yinhe.co/archives/20210401_hugo_theme_stack.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>网站&lt;/a>有详细的customize教程&lt;/li>
&lt;li>这位大神写了&lt;a class="link" href="https://blog.echosec.top/tags/hugo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>很多Hugo很实用的帖子&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
